耳不闻”，也表明策划活动中缺乏女性决策者。 线上跑步社区Run Mummy Run也同意“夺回这些街道”的观点，并表示在这种情况下，塑造一个女性在夜间跑步的形象是不现实的。“这似乎意味着，女性拥有这种奢侈的自由和安全，但遗憾的是，这不是当前的现实。” 对于外界的批评，三星在接受BBC采访时致歉。三星称，“对围绕女性安全的持续讨论无动于衷”从来都不是公司的本意，“我们对外界的反应表示歉意”。三星还称，“‘夜猫子’活动的设计初衷是想传递一个积极的信息：赞美个性和随时锻炼的自由。”发布女性凌晨2点独自跑步广告被批“不切实际”，三星道歉"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ii8PS5uSGwpcMEAMaCDgwMjMyOTg5INzPs5MGMBM4xQJACXIJNTMwNzc4NTMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"237 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ad084d92461f6e4adcf4f5f9b2399371_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1651338850.2293248","card_id":"Q_529712895","target":{"id":529712895,"title":"泽连斯基现在不停找西方要钱，未来会给乌克兰背上巨额债务吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/529712895","type":"question","created":1650765006,"answer_count":298,"follower_count":502,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5548,10715,30738],"comment_count":24,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUIi8PS5uSGwpcMEAMaCDc5OTk1OTg4IM7ZkpMGMBg49gNACnIJNTI5NzEyODk1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"235 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-fe224ba6cd2d6c62b55ad30e2730086a_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1651338850.2298043","card_id":"Q_530688623","target":{"id":530688623,"title":"美国冻结部分俄罗斯富豪私人财产的行为，符合西方标榜的私人财产神圣不可侵犯原则吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/530688623","type":"question","created":1651242675,"answer_count":288,"follower_count":591,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[472,4316,5548,35438,152604],"comment_count":30,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUIi8PS5uSGwpcMEAMaCDgwMjEyOTA1ILPtr5MG